dmca.title: Subpoena Report
dmca.body: I received a letter from SBC and a subpoena from California. These papers said I have been downloading motion pictures and I don't even have any movies on my computer, I never downloaded any either. It also has dates when I "downloaded these movies" and I didn't even have a file sharing system at some of these times and it shows multiple IP addresses. I don't understand why I received this subpoena.
